  "Description": {
    "English": "The <span class=\"name name-technology\">SSV Normandy SR1</span> is a one-of-a-kind 'deep scout' frigate. This legendary ship represents peace and cooperation between races, and commemorates completion of the 'Beachhead' <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Expedition</span>.<br><br>Recruiting this frigate will add it to your fleet. Manage your frigate fleet from a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Fleet Command Room</span> aboard your freighter, and consult your <span class=\"name name-technology\">Navigator</span> to deploy frigates on lucrative expeditions.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">SSV Normandy SR1</span>是独一无二的“深渊侦查”护卫舰。这艘传奇飞船代表种族间的和平与合作，同时纪念了“抢滩”<span class=\"name name-stellar\">远征</span>的完成。<br><br>招募这艘护卫舰，它将加入你的舰队。在货船上的<span class=\"name name-technology\">舰队指挥室</span>管理你的护卫舰队， 与<span class=\"name name-technology\">领航员</span>交谈，在奖励丰厚的远征中部署护卫舰。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">SSV Normandy SR1</span> 是一艘獨一無二的 「深處偵查」巡防艦。此傳奇巡防艦代表了種族間的和平與合作，也紀念了「灘頭」<span class=\"name name-stellar\">探險</span>的完成。<br><br>將此巡防艦招募到你的艦隊。登上貨船的<span class=\"name name-technology\">艦隊指揮處</span>管理你的巡防艦艦隊，並徵詢<span class=\"name name-technology\">領航員</span>的意見，將巡防艦部署到有利可圖的探險中。"
  },
